      "text": "演奏 : 五月天",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 5.26,
      "time_str": "00:05.260",
      "text": "管弦乐团 : 陈建良+五月天",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 6.14,
      "time_str": "00:06.140",
      "text": "管乐 : 黄任贤+赖怡蒨（陈建良+五月天/敬业录音室+288录音室）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 8.78,
      "time_str": "00:08.780",
      "text": "录音助理 : Yasuhiko Miyasaka/河口湖Studio+Shigeki Serizawa/Sound Crew Studio",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 10.53,
      "time_str": "00:10.530",
      "text": "母带后期处理 : 王舒屏/异术录音室",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 13.11,
      "time_str": "00:13.110",
      "text": "走在风中 今天阳光 突然好温柔",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 19.6,
      "time_str": "00:19.600",
      "text": "天的温柔 地的温柔 像你抱着我",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 26.1,
      "time_str": "00:26.100",
      "text": "然后发现你的改变 孤单的今后",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 31.75,
      "time_str": "00:31.750",
      "text": "如果冷 该怎么度过",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 42.3,
      "time_str": "00:42.300",
      "text": "天边风光 身边的我 都不在你眼中",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 48.76,
      "time_str": "00:48.760",
      "text": "你的眼中藏着什么 我从来都不懂",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 55.22,
      "time_str": "00:55.220",
      "text": "没有关系 你的世界 就让你拥有",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 60.94,
      "time_str": "01:00.940",
      "text": "不打扰 是我的温柔",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 71.03,
      "time_str": "01:11.030",
      "text": "不知道 不明了 不想要",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 73.41,
      "time_str": "01:13.410",
      "text": "为什么我的心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 77.56,
      "time_str": "01:17.560",
      "text": "明明是想靠近 却孤单到黎明",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 84.01,
      "time_str": "01:24.010",
      "text": "不知道 不明了 不想要",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 86.4,
      "time_str": "01:26.400",
      "text": "为什么我的心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 90.5,
      "time_str": "01:30.500",
      "text": "那爱情的绮丽 总是在孤单里",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 96.96,
      "time_str": "01:36.960",
      "text": "再把我的最好的爱给你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 103.91,
      "time_str": "01:43.910",
      "text": "不知不觉 不情不愿 又到巷子口",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 110.34,
      "time_str": "01:50.340",
      "text": "我没有哭 也没有笑 因为这是梦",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 116.85,
      "time_str": "01:56.850",
      "text": "没有预兆 没有理由 你真的有说过",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 122.54,
      "time_str": "02:02.540",
      "text": "如果有 就让你自由",
